message.body: Hey love, got a question for ya: who else from here is coming to your house this weekend? Danielle can't come so I figure its dumb to drive all the way up by myself.
Me too! We just found out dans sister and her 2 annoying kids are going up but whatever were gonna party and pretend like they're not there!
Awesome. I want more fireworks too.
We need someone with an out of state id!
